This paper is likely to belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR) category as it deals with candidate retrieval in recommendation systems. It also involves deep learning-based recommenders, which could fall under the categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The paper may also involve Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) and Computer Vision (cs.CV) techniques, depending on the type of recommendation system being used.
